WEBVTT

00:06.141 --> 00:07.960
Previously on Bad Blood...

00:08.077 --> 00:11.778
Number one priority,
taking care of my son.

00:11.846 --> 00:13.813
You are my employee.

00:13.882 --> 00:17.085
I pay you to take care of my family.

00:17.110 --> 00:18.781
No more commission.

00:18.992 --> 00:20.491
I just get a straight 10%.

00:20.560 --> 00:21.725
I already have investors.

00:21.794 --> 00:23.539
Not without the permits, you don't.

00:23.547 --> 00:26.291
Some journalists with nothing
better to do for a couple years,

00:26.315 --> 00:27.949
release a bombshell report

00:28.017 --> 00:30.384
saying the entire city's
construction industry

00:30.453 --> 00:33.257
was totally corrupt
and controlled by the mob.

00:33.890 --> 00:36.691
If we find this to be true,
it will stand no more.

00:36.759 --> 00:37.759
Shit!

00:37.826 --> 00:39.159
I need you to call your father.

00:39.184 --> 00:40.283
Then you're gonna say,

00:40.308 --> 00:41.828
"Dad, I hear you got a bad cough."

00:41.988 --> 00:43.320
And then you'll insist

00:43.398 --> 00:45.232
that he goes to see the prison doctor.

00:45.585 --> 00:47.123
Why do you have pictures of my family?

00:47.148 --> 00:48.718
You work at a prison, right?

00:48.804 --> 00:50.704
- To cancer!
- To cancer!

00:50.772 --> 00:52.570
To my son, coming home.

00:52.671 --> 00:55.398
I am Vito, right now!

00:55.445 --> 00:58.813
All we have is our name and
he is using it for himself.

00:58.882 --> 01:00.757
I respect that name more than my own.

01:07.691 --> 01:08.757
When's the funeral?

01:08.825 --> 01:09.825
In three days.

01:09.893 --> 01:11.725
You're not going to let me bury my son?

